{"type": "article", "id": 22252, "title": "扭曲旋转吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061530335RTIdojqXfLnaOAB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这一系列的吊灯名为 Palindrome，来自美国一个擅长做灯具的设计工作室 rich brilliant willing。它有 2、4、6、8 一共四种型号，对应了灯的数量。结构上使用可组合的钢管臂，让吊灯可以成为闭合的圆环或缠绕扭曲的线条，极具雕塑感，也可以适应不同的空间。这款的灯的光线也是可调的，从白色到琥珀色，<a href=\"http://richbrilliantwilling.com/collections/palindrome\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153031CVfOa05zZuSgov1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615303212qOxYJ4LcG3rUeC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.78728606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153032F1JTX6mLQCNjnW5I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84229829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153033ceINVmL5BdaHj8EC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}